{"tid":1029532,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[三國］其實孫吳有無機會北伐成功","createTime":"2019-02-20T10:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T16:11:50.000Z","uid":89538,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9d59de387eca2dd8528955e2a905a26ea1078aa6","tid":1029532,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"明明有地， 荊 江東<br />\n有將 （遠比蜀多人才）<br />\n有兵 幾十萬打合淝<br />\n<br />\n雖然有四大氏族 私兵既問題<br />\n但至少都叫出到兵<br />\n將領 都督 幾代都勁 周郎 呂蒙 陸遜 （魯肅主張平衡 暫時唔計）<br />\n唔計一大堆將領<br />\n<br />\n長時間經營 但赤壁之後 基本上打親都輸<br />\n只係偷襲關羽自大 火燒劉備智障<br />\n就好似中國人咁 最叻打自己友<br />\n到底孫吳想點？"},{"pid":"761859e7dbe47faecb68878ef54abfaaafcf8d5b","tid":1029532,"uid":230703,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"佢地低能打劉備，兩家合作可能有機。 自相殘殺唔輸都難"},{"pid":"393d818e22f77f94a81ef1cefea96b5af71a3446","tid":1029532,"uid":228963,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f5910e2cabe28734f256f334a4640c631492887","tid":1029532,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"不嬲都只想偏安"},{"pid":"695bb97bdd0b1c8650a8e87241b5250ad42ea90d","tid":1029532,"uid":32486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"海軍北上打平原戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60ff9c87324ed641e588e662c8ed9c78cf56944","tid":1029532,"uid":89538,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"點解孫家咁多年 只係識水戰<br />\n<br />\n張遼幾百人偷襲可以打殘孫權<br />\n到底陸戰有幾廢？<br />\n<br />\n曹操都叫操到下水軍<br />\n赤壁都叫輸得心甘命抵<br />\n孫家d陸軍做緊乜？<br />\n生存時間最長 但乜7都練唔到"},{"pid":"451e0e727a661c931fd2937ad3dc221e13cd757a","tid":1029532,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"吳連北伐都冇嘗試過，你覺得點解？"},{"pid":"5c619de6636112a48f1222c76b66907b23da8563","tid":1029532,"uid":186431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc